     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'creemore-spring-brewery', 'Creemore Spring Brewery', 'The unique quality and flavour of Creemore Springs Premium Lager begins by selecting the finest possible ingredients. It all starts with the source of pure spring water that our beer is named after. The spring is located in a bedrock of limestone cooled and shaded by a hardwood forest just outside the town of Creemore. Only three other natural ingredients go into our great beer: malted barley, select hops and yeast. Malted barley is a high grade of barley that has been germinated and dried. This modifies the starch for the brewing process. Our selected Saaz hops from the Czech Republic are a &lsquo;spicy&rsquo; bud that imparts just the right characteristic bitterness and aroma.', 1987,
