     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'dickersbach-brewing-company', 'Dickersbach Brewing Company', 'A long long time ago, in a far away place called North Carolina it all started. My great friend, and then neighbor, Randy and I decided it was time to start brewing beer since we could not longer get our then favorite brew in the stores. Our first beer was aptly named &quot;Girly Beer&quot; and was light and refreshing.<br><br>From there the brews continued until we were out of storage space. Our paths separated, but we each continued brewing. My brother Mike, soon took to brewing also and has been an avid brewer for many years now.<br><br>Background experience comes from homebrewing, being head brewer at Hal and Mal''s in Jackson, MS, and head brewer at Riverhorse, in Lambertville, NJ.', 1992,
