     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'doodle-brewing-company', 'Doodle Brewing Company', 'The Doodle Brewing Company was started by Nick Vaughn in 2008. Nick graduated from the University of Missouri-Columbia with a degree in Chemical Engineering. After graduation, Nick got a call from the Harpoon Brewery in Boston and they were willing to give him a shot. While he was working out east, he enjoyed the superb beer culture and variety of beers available in New England. But he knew that he would one day return to Missouri. Finally, after three years, probably too many beers, and the addition of his son, Nick finally got his chance to come back to Missouri. He worked at a small brewpub in Kansas City called The 75th Street Brewery where he was able to experiment with many different beer styles and brewing techniques. Again after a f ew years, Nick grew restless. While working at a brewpub was fun and enjoyable, it just had too many other distractions from his true passions... Brewing beer, drinking beer and spreading the word about craft beer.<br>So he started the Doodle Brewing Company with every intention of brewing beers and beer styles that explore the boundries of flavor. He''s probably sitting in front of his brewhouse right now with a beer enjoying what he''s doing because he''s making beer for you.', 2008,
      '', 'http://www.doodlebrewing.com/', '600 Haines Drive', '',
      'Liberty', 'Missouri', '64068', 'US', '2014',
        '2011-12-12T23:58:09.653-0800', true);

