     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'east-end-brewing-company', 'East End Brewing Company', 'If you don&rsquo;t already know, let me say right up front that we are a microbrewery in the true sense of the word, and not a brewpub. We leave the serving to the experts at the fine establishments who pour our brews around town. So please, don&rsquo;t take it personally if we don&rsquo;t ask you to come on over for a beer. It&rsquo;s not you, or that shirt you&rsquo;re wearing that puts us off. It&rsquo;s because there&rsquo;s really no place inside our brewery for you to sit down, have a sandwich and enjoy a fresh pint of tasty brew &ndash; though, I personally have been known to do this very thing from time to time. When you have your own brewery, maybe you can do this too.<br><br><br>That said, for those that want to get a closer look,  you can always come out during our &quot;Growler Hours&quot; . We can show you around the place a bit, and you can even take some beer home with you. Here''s a map to help you find the place.', null,
