     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'flying-monkeys-craft-brewery', 'Flying Monkeys Craft Brewery', 'The Flying Monkeys Craft Brewery is locally run by a few beer-lovin&rsquo; friends and a family of unwavering Beer Disciples right in the heart of downtown Barrie, Ontario. We&rsquo;re brewing towards a day when Ontario beer lovers won&rsquo;t have to look south of the border for artisanal beers made with enough hops to rip your tongue from your mouth; for edgy brews with alcohol contents that rival spirits; for rich beers aged in bourbon barrels; or creative ales brewed with strange and interesting ingredients. Our philosophy? Keep the Microbrewery Revolution going --and let the Brewscape of Ontario show how complex and versatile craft brewing can actually be. Bottoms up, and Release the Flying Monkeys!', null,
