     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'franconia-brewing-company', 'Franconia Brewing Company', 'With a brewing heritage that dates back to the 1800''s, Franconia Brewing Company is more than just a local brewery, it''s the essence of the true Bavarian brew. By combining the local accessibility of North Texas with our German/heritage/history we are going to provide the fine people of North Texas with a taste of some of the most genuine and freshest Bavarian beer available. <br><br>Franconia Brewing Company not only delivers the freshest brews to your favorite restaurants, pubs, and taverns, we also have adopted many green practices to help improve the environmental concerns in North Dallas.', 2003,
