     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'franziskaner', 'Franziskaner', 'Franziskaner dates back to the oldest privately-owned brewery in Munich in 1363. Open up our history books and cast a glimpse at the eventful history of our brewery.<br><br><br>The Franziskaner-Leist Brewery and the Spaten Brewery, likewise owned by the Sedlmayr family, unite to form a single joint stock company, the ''Gabriel und Joseph Sedlmayr Spaten-Franziskaner-Leistbr&auml;u AG'', in order to combat the economic problems of the crisis-ridden postwar years and to capitalize on synergies.<br><br>&lt;a href=&quot;http://brewerydb.com/brewery/info/id/1176&quot;&gt; Spaten-Franziskaner-Leistbr&auml;u AG&lt;/a&gt;', 1363,
      '+49 (0)89 - 5200 0', 'http://www.franziskaner.com/', 'Marsstrasse 46+48', '',
      'Munich', 'Bavaria', 'D-80335', 'DE', '1410',
        '2011-12-12T23:59:19.770-0800', true);

