     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'georgetown-brewing-company', 'Georgetown Brewing Company', 'Georgetown Brewing Company, a Seattle microbrewery and brewer of Manny''s Pale Ale. We''re a draft beer only production brewery, which means that all we do is make beer and fill kegs. Sorry, no brewpub, but we do have a retail shop where you can pick up kegs to go, growlers, and perhaps get a taste of our newest beer before it''s released. Or you could be social and get out to your favorite local watering hole. If they don''t have our beer on tap, let us know and we''ll do our best to pester ''em into submission. Do we bottle? Not yet but we never say never. Right now we''re focused on doing one thing right... draft beer. Cheers!', 2002,
