     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'glenora-springs-brewery-ltd', 'Glenora Springs Brewery Ltd.', '.S.B. is owned and operated by the McKinney brothers, John and Jim. We are located on the shores of the Bay of Quinte at Glenora near Adolphus Reach. The region is steeped in tradition dating back to the mid 1700''s when Prince Edward County was colonized by United Empire Loyalists. Behind our hill lies the fabled Lake on the Mountain and right out our lane you can catch a lift on the scenic Glenora Ferry to Kingston and the 1000 Islands. Our focus is simple; crafting excellent beers with no compromise. We are proud to provide a balanced but diverse line of three products representing classic brewing styles.  G.S.B. uses only the finest malts and imported hops and is committed to small batch sizes to insure consistent quality. We are fiercel y loyal to an independent philosophy in brewing and all the arts in general..', null,
