     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'great-crescent-brewery', 'Great Crescent Brewery', 'The Great Crescent Brewery beers are made with all malt, fresh hops and whole ingredients. Every beer is hand-crafted in small batches using traditional brewing methods. We package our beer in self-pressurizing mini-kegs that hold the equivalent of a case of beer, half&ndash;gallon refillable growler bottles and 1/6 barrel (5 gallon) kegs that can be used in commercial and home draft systems. Some of our specialty beers, like our Cherry Ale, will only be available in limited quantities.<br>We are a production brewery that sells beer right from the premises. Although we don&rsquo;t currently have a tasting room where we can sell beer by the glass &ndash; we will be offering samples to help you decide which beer to purchase.<br><br>We are ope n to the public Wednesday-Friday 2pm to 7pm, Saturday 12 (noon) to 7pm and Sunday 12 (noon) to 4pm. You can purchase our beers outside of the brewery at The Pour House in Aurora, Indiana, Bakers Discount Liquors in Rising Sun, Indiana and Whitey&rsquo;s in Lawrenceburg, Indiana. We are also available on draft at Bourbons Bar &amp; Grill in Lawrenceburg, Indiana.', 2008,
