     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'great-northern-brewing-company', 'Great Northern Brewing Company', 'Located in Whitefish, Montana the Great Northern Brewing Company offers the finest quality ales and lagers in a variety of year-round and seasonal styles. Through the use of a traditional &quot;Gravity Flow&quot; arrangement, our beers are made in the tradition of artisan brewing with one of the most sophisticated brew houses for its size in the entire country.<br><br>Started by Minott Wessinger, the great-great grandson of Henry Weinhard, the Great Northern Brewery was built in 1994 to brew Black Star Double Hopped Golden Lager. The Great Northern Brewing Company continues brewing a wide variety of craft-beers.<br><br>Whitefish, Montana was chosen as the home for the Great Northern Brewery because of its rugged and beautiful surroundings,  the excellent water, and the unique history of the Flathead Valley.', 1994,
