     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'hawaii-nui-brewing', 'Hawai''i Nui Brewing', 'At Hawai&lsquo;i Nui Brewing, we&rsquo;re passionate about craft beer. We brew small batches of our all-natural ales and lagers from the finest barley malt, wheat, hops and yeast.  We are committed to local production in Hawai&lsquo;i.  <br><br>Our uniquely well balanced Island Style beer is perfect for your time in Paradise!<br><br>What is Island Style? To those of us who call Hawai&rsquo;i home, it&rsquo;s all about balance. Working hard, sure. But when pau hana time comes, it&rsquo;s about friends and family. Heeding the call of the sun and sand, surf and sea. Tasting freshness. Celebrating music. Stopping at sunset. Resting easy at night. Appreciating life&rsquo;s detours&ndash;what we call holo holo time. Living life as it should be.', null,
