     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'highland-brewing-company', 'Highland Brewing Company', 'Highland Brewing Company began in the basement of Barley''s Taproom in downtown Asheville, North Carolina in 1994. Through the years the company has grown from a three person operation to a staff of 17, from about 4,000 to 35,000 square feet, and from a capacity to brew 2,000 barrels annually to almost 20,000 (that&rsquo;s 620,000 gallons). Those of you who saw the old brewery may remember the retrofitted dairy equipment we used. We held on to two of those tanks in our move to the East Asheville location. Alongside those, we have new fermentation and brite beer tanks to go with our 50 barrel brew house. We finally have the space to play around with seasonal beers, high gravity brews, cask ales, and whatever else the brewers dream up. Highlan d currently supplies both Carolinas and parts of Georgia,Tennessee, Florida, Alabama and Virgina. Thanks for your support!', 1994,
