     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'la-cagole', 'La Cagole', 'Cagole the creeks is a girl; It is the brainchild of two childhood friends at a cocktail in a shed Sormiou.<br><br>Both nostalgic old Marseille and beer lovers, the cronies have devised a beer the color of the Old Port of Pagnol. A golden beer with a Provencal accent, that Caesar and Marius could have gone to the terrace of the Bar of the Navy.<br><br>This adventure is also a way to honor the elders that were the glorious Phoenix beers, brewed Velten and Marx in Marseille', null,
      '+33 (0)4 91 37 00 30', 'http://www.lacagole.com/', '3, Impasse du pistou', '',
      'Marseille', '', '13009', 'FR', '1422',
        '2011-12-13T00:01:58.574-0800', true);

