     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'langham-brewery', 'Langham Brewery', 'Langham is a traditional craft micro-brewery. We have a restored 10 barrel steam heated plant, updated with the latest control and measurement equipment to ensure consistent and flavoursome beers every brew.<br><br>What sets us apart?<br><br>First we only use the finest quality ingredients - water, floor malted barley and aroma hops, sourced as far as possible from local English suppliers.<br><br>And second, we cask conditions our beer. For every landlord this means a longer shelf life than beer from conditioning tanks. And for the real ale people it means better, fresher tasting beer.<br><br>Visitors are always welcome to the brewery shop for offsales - from two pints to a firkin for that special occasion, party or wedding. The brewery is  open on Tuesday, Thursday and Saturday, but please ring in advance to avoid disapointment.', 2005,
