     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'left-coast-brewing', 'Left Coast Brewing', 'Left Coast Brewing Company was formed in 2004 with the original intent to brew beer for the Oggi''s Pizza and Brewing Company restaurants. Since then, we have expanded our operation to include the production of beer under the Left Coast Brewing Company Brand. Our main focus for the Left Coast beers are American style ales. We do however add new styles as part of our seasonal program and have one Belgian tripel ale.<br><br>We brew, bottle and keg everything in house at our San Clemente facility and our team is dedicated to the perfection of our product.', null,
