     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'lompoc-brewing', 'Lompoc Brewing', 'Lompoc Brewing has been producing handcrafted beer in Portland, Ore. since 1996. The Lompoc family of pubs includes New Old Lompoc, Hedge House, Oaks Bottom, Fifth Quadrant and Sidebar. Find our beers in bottles and on draft throughout the city.<br><br>Lompoc Brewing has been producing handcrafted ales and lagers since 1996. The Lompoc Empire of brewpubs began with the New Old Lompoc at 1616 NW 23rd Ave in Portland. It has since expanded to include three more locations: Hedge House (3412 SE Division), Oaks Bottom (1621 SE Bybee) and Fifth Quadrant, better known as 5Q (3901 N Williams), where it also opened a second brewery to accommodate the demand.<br><br>Lompoc Fifth Quadrant also has a barrel tasting room - The Sidebar - where beer lover s can enjoy a variety of barrel aged and seasonal specialty beer that are only available at the tasting room in limited quantities. The Sidebar is open Fridays from 4 PM to 10 PM and Saturdays from 2 to 10 PM. <br><br>All Lompoc restaurants feature an excellent array of Northwest pub fare with a great selection of soups, salads, sandwiches and entrees. Each restaurant boasts its own menu, and claims its own specialty - the New Old Lompoc serves up the best clam chowder in town, while Oaks Bottom is famous for its Tatchos - nachos made with tater tots. All four locations offer fantastic outdoor patios and decks.', 1996,
