     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'low-brau', 'Low Brau', 'Low Brau LLC is a Washington, DC based nano brewery created by Steven Sorrell in response to the current American Craftbrewing atmosphere. After visting breweries around the world, Steven noticed a lack of crisp refreshing session style beers brewed here in the US, so in 2010, the seeds of Low Brau were planted. <br><br>With a background in the food industry and many years of beer research, it was only natural for Steven to start brewing at home, and wasn''t long before he started creating his own recipes. Now a year later, Low Brau continues to move forward, with plans to open it''s doors within the District in the next year. <br><br>Low Brau''s beers are German inspired, following the guidelines set fourth by the Rheinheitsgebot Purity Law a nd high quality ingredients. Each beer is hand crafted and brewed in small batches to maintain quality over quantity. <br><br>Low Brau strongly believes in &quot;Embracing Simplicity&quot;.', 2010,
