     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'nowhere-brewing-company', 'Nowhere Brewing Company', 'Nowhere Brewing Company is not quite an official brewery...yet. With 10 years of local brewing behind us, it''s our goal to establish a nano brewery and taproom where the great people on the North Shore can enjoy local beer. Until then look for us at local beer events and remember, great beer comes out of Nowhere.<br><br>Nowhere Brewing Company is looking to build a great group of investors that are excited about our beer, and bring more small batch beer to the North Shore. Know of someone that is looking for an incredible investment opportunity? Send them my email, chris@nowherebrewingcompany.com. We are eager to share with our community and enthused about involving all of you in our journey.', 2011,
