     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'pizza-port-brewing--carlsbad', 'Pizza Port Brewing - Carlsbad', 'Welcome to the 2009 GABF Large Brewpub of the Year and Intergalactic Headquarters for the Pizza Port Empire!<br>Opened in 1997, Pizza Port Carlsbad sits at the corner of Carlsbad Village Drive and Roosevelt Street in the heart of beautiful Carlsbad.<br>Just blocks from the beach, Pizza Port Carlsbad&rsquo;s head brewer Jeff Bagby and his team ensure that there&rsquo;s always be plenty of great, fresh brewed craft beers (both their own and plenty of guest beers) on tap no matter when you decide to drop by. Oh, and right next door you&rsquo;ll find the famous Pizza Port Bottle Shop with over 600 bottles of beer from every corner of the Earth!', 1997,
