     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'roanoke-railhouse-brewing-company', 'Roanoke Railhouse Brewing Company', '&quot;When it comes to making great beer, Roanoke Railhouse has a 1 track mind.&quot;<br><br><br>Anyone can brew beer. Brewing great beer, however, requires science and technology and we have what it takes.<br><br>Our brewmaster, Ryan Worthington has an International Diploma in Brewing Technology. He is a graduate of the World Brewing Academy/Siebel Institute of Technology in Chicago and the <br>Doemens Academy in Grafelfing, Germany<br><br>Our optimized, custom built brewhouse gives our Brewmaster the right tools to brew great beer. This combination of talent and tools is our recipe for success.', null,
