     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'rock-art-brewery', 'Rock Art Brewery', 'Matt began the brewery in the basement of our home in 1997. Wow! I can''t believe I let him do that! His first beer was Whitetail Ale. A nice crisp refreshing golden ale. I was really enjoying wheat beers at the time. I guess that''s why I let him start Rock Art! The Brewery was ready to leave home and move to it''s own place down the road in Morrisville, VT in 2001. We are still located there and now have a terrific space for people to come and visit. Come on by and say hello!<br><br>Our Mission is to offer our friends and family a wonderful beer at the end of the day!', null,
