     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'saugatuck-brewing-company', 'Saugatuck Brewing Company', 'Saugatuck Brewing Co. is a traditional Irish style pub that features quality beer, wine, food, and service. We have twelve unique brews made by our Brewmaster that are served in the Pub and bottled and distributed throughout the mid-west. <br><br>We feature the only brew-on-site facility in West Michigan. With five copper kettles, an array of natural ingredients, and over 100 recipes, we invite you and your friends to be the Brewmaster for a day. Create your own unique ale and return in two weeks to bottle 5 cases of fresh beer with a custom label of your choice.<br><br>The Bier Hall is our multi-purpose banquet facility complete with stage and lights. This venue can be rented for weddings, receptions, reunions, corporate events and concert s. The Bier Hall can accommodate up to 200-seated guests. Catering and bar services are included.', null,
