     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'sly-fox-brewhouse-and-eatery', 'Sly Fox Brewhouse and Eatery', 'A full production brewery and accompanying restaurant opened in 2004 by the owners of Sly Fox Brewhouse &amp; Eatery in nearby Phoenixville. The 20bbl brewhouse packages a wide range of beers in 12oz cans, 22oz bottles and 750ml bottles. Pikeland Pils, a multiple GABF Gold Medal Winner, and O''Reilly''s Stout, a nitro-poured, draught-only beer named after brewer Brian O''Reilly''s grandfather are among its most popular beers, on and off premises, as are such Belgian-style delights as Incubus Tripel, Ichor Quadrupel, Saison Vos &amp; Black Raspberry Reserve. Sly Fox is also noted for its Bock Beers (see listing for the Phoenixville pub for more details) and annual Christmas Ale.', 1995,
