     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'the-bruery', 'The Bruery', 'A small craft brewery located in Orange County, California. Our simple but often confusing name is a fusion of ''brewery'' with our family name, Rue.<br><br>Our calling is to create beers with character and depth using the simplest and purest of means. We do not filter or pasteurize our beers. All of our bottled beers gain carbonation through bottle conditioning, allowing carbonation to naturally occur through a secondary bottle fermentation. We strive to use unconventional ingredients, and we will proudly state what we put in our beers.', null,
