     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'the-commons-brewery', 'The Commons Brewery', 'Formerly known as Beetje Brewery<br><br>The Commons Brewery started in Mike Wright&rsquo;s garage in Southeast Portland. A truenano brewery to be sure.-you can read more about that toward the bottom of this page.<br><br>After a short stint in the garage brewery, Mike decided to expand the operation to a 7bbl brewhouse and a new space. That work began in the summer of 2011 and should wrap up in the Fall of 2011.<br><br>The Commons strives to make well executed beers , often with yeasts originating from Belgium, that enable or enhance social interaction. For the consumer the focus should not be on the beer, rather in their friends and family they have gathered with.', null,
