     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'the-stable', 'The Stable', 'The Stable is a brewpub and micro-distillery proudly located in the Benton Park Neighborhood of St. Louis on the northeast corner of Cherokee and Lemp. The StableOur building was where the draft horses for the historic Lemp Brewery were kept, thus the name. We are honored to once again be brewing beer on these grounds for the first time since Prohibition. In addition to our own brews, we serve up the best craft beer from across the country and the world. We have 36 rotating taps so you''ll always have new selections to choose from each time you visit. We also serve great appetizers, sandwiches, and some say the best pizza in St. Louis. We hope to see you soon.<br><br>Our Brewery: We specialize in brewing traditional German lagers, using only  the finest barley malt, hops, and yeast from Germany. Our styles include Helles, Marzen, Dunkel, Rauchbier, and Zoigl. All of our beer is brewed and served right on site. The person having a beer next to you at the bar may be one of our brewers.', null,
