     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'von-jakob-brewery', 'Von Jakob Brewery', 'As Von Jakob Vineyard, we have brought exceptional wines to the Southern Illinois area and beyond for over 15 years. Now, we are excited to introduce Von Jakob Brewery, complete with hand-crafted brews, made exclusively at our Orchard location in Alto Pass, Illinois.<br><br>Offering eight styles of beer ranging from our crisp, clean, lightly-hopped American Pilsner to our rich, dark Stout, you are sure to find a beer that delights your palate. Or, if you are having trouble choosing just one, we offer a flight of all eight delicious beers. We also have a great selection of domestic beers as well as premium beers from around the world for your enjoyment.<br><br>And for our wine enthusiasts out there, do not worry &ndash; our winery isn&rsquo; t going anywhere. We just thought we would offer you a different libation of choice, should you want to explore it.<br><br>We sincerely thank you for your support over the years, and we welcome you to come and experience this next adventure with us!', null,
