     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'wynkoop-brewing-company-denver', 'Wynkoop Brewing Company Denver', 'Colorado&rsquo;s first brewpub, Wynkoop Brewing Company was founded in 1988 by a group of young entrepreneurs and urban pioneers led by current Denver Mayor John Hickenlooper.<br><br>Our brewpub&rsquo;s hallmarks -- highly acclaimed small-batch beers, high quality food &amp; service, the city&rsquo;s best pool hall and our glorious 1888 building -- helped make us a major catalyst for the revival of Lower Downtown Denver.<br><br>Today Wynkoop Brewing Company is a beer-blessed Denver institution, a must-visit Colorado landmark and one of the nation&rsquo;s most revered craft breweries.<br><br>We&rsquo;re also one of the city&rsquo;s best places for private and corporate events. We&rsquo;ve hosted everything from Democratic National Convention  parties to beer festivals, weddings and company conferences. (All with great beer and food.)<br><br>Today we&rsquo;re expanding our downtown brewing efforts to deliver more of our ambitious, artisan-style craft beer to Denver&rsquo;s best beer outlets. Look for cans of our Rail Yard Ale in local stores and kegs of all of our beers at the area&rsquo;s top bars and restaurants.', 1988,
