     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'the-3-brewers', 'The 3 Brewers', 'First sip, first revelation, you tell yourself that The 3 Brewers beer has a unique taste...and you are right! Because in addition to being brewed on-site (i.e a few meters away from where you are sitting), this beer is the result of an ancestral heritage. A shared love of the foam, transmitted from generation to generation for over two centuries. Cheers! The story truly begins in the early twentieth century, in Lille, where 3 brewers (already.) joined forces to found a brewery that would become one of the most important French breweries. In 1985, their descendants, trained at a good school and sharing the same love for this golden beverage, embarked on their adventure.', 1986,
