     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'cahoots-brewing', 'Cahoots Brewing', 'Cahoots Brewing is a unique brewery in the sense that we do not have facilities. We focus on creating collaboration-style beers with local craft breweries. Our beers strive for high-gravity, unique tastes, and exceptional quality. As we grow, we will develop forums where honorary brewmasters can submit recipes for different categories of beers that we are planning to brew. Essentially, our fans can be in cahoots with us as we make awesome beers. Our mission is to create a community brewery that works alongside other breweries to create high gravity (high ABV), high flavor, high quality beers. By emphasizing the community aspect of the brewery, we will draw in beer advocates who want to feel like a part of a brewery. We will also give back t o the communities where our beers are made.', 2014,
      '', 'http://cahootsbrewing.com/', '137 South Grove Avenue', '',
      'Oak Park', 'Illinois', '60302', 'USA', '',
        null, true);

