     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'black-rocks-brewery', 'Black Rocks Brewery', 'In 2010, David and Andy were looking down the barrel of economic downsizing in their industry. Looking at it as an opportunity instead of a problem, the two set out to take their basement hobby to a new level. The dream of all home brewers; to go &quot;legit&quot; and open a commercial brewery, presented itself as a once in a lifetime opportunity. The two agreed upon a Nano Brewery (less than 2bbl brewhouse). Although they were hopeful it would be well received, they had no idea the amount of interest the local community had for craft beers. They have been slowly growing ever since.', 2010,
