     VALUES ('BREWERY', 'atlas-cider-company', 'Atlas Cider Company', 'ATLAS Cider Co. produces authentic hard cider fermented from 100% fresh pressed fruit from our region. Partnering with northwest farmers to source our fruit has been a priority of ours from the beginning. Our ciders start with a base of Northwest varieties that are pressed to achieve a balance of sweetness, tartness, and dryness in our blends. Using cold pressed technology and first-rate fruit allows us to retain the apple and fruits delicate aroma and flavors. Our ciders are crafted in the heart of the Northwest in Bend, OR.', 2007,
